Author: soad42rus
Title: [ANN] [PRE-ICO]+[ICO]+[Blockchain]- "Sorgin"
Body: The other tests of the “Sorgin” agent were organized at the “Farm enterprise of Malashina” in 2017. The “Sorgin” agent was tested on plantlet of “Lobelia”, “Salvia”, “Begonia”,” Petunia”, “Tagetes”.                    https://c.radikal.ru/c36/1806/b4/ac756630714c.jpg  К-control plantlet ( no agent) B-(with the “Sorgin” agent); The picture was made after 6 days of using the agent.  The characteristics of the high-grade plantlet are next: a typical color, proportional organs of plants and flower bud. It means after transplantation to a hothouse or to a sagged earth the plants will continue their growth without reclamation disease.
